Package: rmdCore
Type: Package
Date: 2019-05-16
Title: Run templates analysis isolated in single reporsitories
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lorena Pantano
Maintainer: Lorena Pantano <lorena.pantano@gmail.com>
Description: Following the same logic than nextflow, where
    a pipeline can be in GitHub repositories, it will download
    the template and run the workflow with custom parameters.
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
